Version: 3.0.4

Add shippingModeId porperty on product document
Add selectbyproduct porperty on shippingfilter document
Add virtualproduct document

For use virtualproduct secure download add this config in your config/project.xml
<config>
	<modules>		
		<media>
			<secureMediaStrategyClass>
				<entry name="virtualproduct">catalog_VirtualProductSecuremediaStrategy</entry>
				...

				